      <p>In the following exercises, an invertible function <m>f(x)</m> is given along with a point that lies on its graph. Using <xref ref="thm_deriv_inverse_functions">Theorem</xref>, evaluate <m>\left(f^{-1}\right)'(x)</m> at the indicated value.</p>
